                            <comment id="356725" author="lflis" created="Fri, 16 Dec 2022 17:14:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Andreas, thank you for pointing this out. You are right indeed.&#160; Let&apos;s close this one&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="356715" author="adilger" created="Fri, 16 Dec 2022 16:26:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t think this is a bug. O_DIRECT requires read/write be sized and aligned on 4096-byte boundaries. The ior-hard-write is doing 47008-byte writes, so this is not expected to work. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
